		<title>14Indoor Recreation</title>
		<content> South Square and the Community Centre 
 provide many indoor activities, such  
 as a Drama Club, a Senior Wayfarers'  
 Group (walks around the Thornton      
 area), a Townswomen's Guild, a        
 Disabled Association and the Thornton 
 Veterans' Association. Many other     
 groups for the elderly also meet in   
 these two buildings. There are several
 youth organisations, such as the      
 Thornton Youth Theatre, Thornton      
 Scouts and Guides Groups, and a Youth 
 Club. Thornton also has an active     
 Peace Group.                          
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
